== About

This script is used to generate a templated email while making introductions. Written by Siddarth Chandrasekaran in 2011.

Usage:
       ./handshake PERSON1 PERSON2

== Usage

    $ ./handshake Bob Alice

Subject: Bob, Alice; Alice, Bob

    Just wanted to put you two in touch with each other.

    Bob, Alice is

    Alice, Bob is

    I'll let you two take it from here -- no need to cc me on your conversation. :-)